{
  "texts": [
    "Most studies in this manuscript comprise a combination of retrospective and prospective study designs.",
    "Over time, we expect more prospectively designed clinical trials to emerge.",
    "Our results suggest that implementing AI technologies can enhance operational efficiency for hospital systems, with notable improvements observed in reducing the length of stay through AI-augmented decision-making by healthcare providers.",
    "Furthermore, these AIaugmented workflows may potentially influence clinical outcomes positively.",
    "However, our study did not address the impact of AI implementation on costs and clinical outcomes, primarily due to the nascent nature of AI technology, with outcome and cost studies expected soon."
  ]
}